7:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both Replit AI and Sweep AI share a solid foundation of core features including Code Generation, Debugging, Multi Language. Where Replit AI pulls ahead is with exclusive access to Autocomplete and Chat, which can be a deciding factor for teams that rely on these capabilities. On the other hand, Sweep AI uniquely offers Code Review and Refactoring, giving it an edge for users who prioritize these areas. \n\nLooking at user ratings, Replit AI holds an overall score of 7/10 and an ease of use score of 9/10, while Sweep AI scores 6/10 overall and 7/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
8:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, Replit AI offers a more budget-friendly entry point at $25/mo, compared to Sweep AI's starting price of $480/mo. Both platforms offer free plans, which is great for testing before committing. Replit AI's free tier and Sweep AI's free tier each have their own limitations, so it is worth evaluating both to see which free offering better matches your initial needs."}]]}]
